title: LIVESTREAM: KYLE RITTENHOUSE TESTIFIES! | Guest Ed Durr | Louder with Crowder
description:
Is it time for a national divorce? Crowder looks at all the reasons to tell liberals, “It’s not you, it’s me. But really it’s you.” We also update you on the Rittenhouse trial and discuss the latest nonsense from Colin Kaepernick. All this and special guest state Senator-elect Edward Durr (R-N.J.).#RittenhouseTrial #ColinKaepernick #KyleRittenhouse
